~FT+-----------------------------------------------------------------------------+
~FT   Command~RS  : preview                                   ~FTPODnuts
~FT+-----------------------------------------------------------------------------+

~FT   Usage~RS    : preview [<picturefile>] 

   This command allows you to preview an ascii picture . An error is
   displayed if you try to view a picture that does not exist.  
   Also, typing .preview on its own will list out all available pictures.

~FT+-----------------------------------------------------------------------------+
~FT   See also~RS : ppicture picture
~FT+-----------------------------------------------------------------------------+
